{"tid":533362,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"分手之後 覺得唔會同到其他人一齊","createTime":"2018-01-18T16:29:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-22T15:40:37.000Z","uid":18863,"like":199,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"013c63f037372dc42fe8878383869bb8fe807c22","tid":533362,"uid":18863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T16:29:43.000Z","msg":"同之前男朋友拍咗8年拖左右，一齊供一層樓<br />\n但佢同公司女同事背住我上床，然後仲想同我爭間屋<br />\n有興趣可以起底睇返...<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然依家已經放低咗好多 亦都有啲好好嘅男人有想同我發展<br />\n但我每次諗到將來同要拍拖就覺得好驚 好攰 透唔到氣<br />\n每樣嘢都好似有佢嘅影子咁樣\b<br />\n我以為時間可以沖淡一切  但都過咗一段時間<br />\n幾時先可以變返正常.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d824e7addda8396a0621aa692c3e58b2f476f82","tid":533362,"uid":76735,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T16:32:54.000Z","msg":"總會遇到岩你既人 幫你醫返好<br />\n加油"},{"pid":"f874a52a29d7edc960ec6717a65d501e8fed4ba1","tid":533362,"uid":18863,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"1d824e7addda8396a0621aa692c3e58b2f476f82","tid":533362,"uid":76735,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T16:32:54.000Z","msg":"總會遇到岩你既人 幫你醫返好<br />\n加油"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T16:34:29.000Z","msg":"好辛苦 好想人生從新開始<br />\n件事好似完唔到咁 依家仲會有朋友問我關於佢嘅事<br />\n我好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想去一個無人識我嘅地方 然後重新開始生活"},{"pid":"84318ad95220af762dec6c42ea10c60c2431fa7a","tid":533362,"uid":51978,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T16:36:37.000Z","msg":"八年都未結婚 慘 同情你"},{"pid":"62397b2fdd22d426839a64b4677f8b1ddec0dcc5","tid":533362,"uid":141789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f874a52a29d7edc960ec6717a65d501e8fed4ba1","tid":533362,"uid":18863,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"1d824e7addda8396a0621aa692c3e58b2f476f82","tid":533362,"uid":76735,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,