491fb7b408b67dd1485510f039628da024b4","tid":533362,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T17:52:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00c33b6dfeb7fc8cf7c8f43a4587b4265baac4e2","tid":533362,"uid":31419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T18:32:47.000Z","msg":"溫絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">攬攬</span></span>"},{"pid":"aad27736726eebcfc628ff64fe8f00e852c0fe8f","tid":533362,"uid":33041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T18:59:45.000Z","msg":"溫絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當時有追晒咁多個post<br />\n重發現男朋友曾經留言，話睇完個post先發現原來自己做嘅野真係會好hurt個ex（應該係溝女之類嘅野，佢冇講清楚），當時重有絲打鬧佢<br />\n雖然我係現任，但諗起佢呃過我話同ex一齊嘅時候絕對專一，加上佢成日講大話俾我發現<br />\n就覺得好傷心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n八年感情真係唔易，太多回憶，真係俾多啲時間自己沉澱下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e7685b7343c9aa054ea7c363335ade7c3dcf2b1","tid":533362,"uid":104054,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T20:11:15.000Z","msg":"初初分手真係灰到一個點<br />\n灰爆頹爆喊爆 成日嘆息 好想返到過去 <br />\n<br />\n後尾經過一班大同 中同 既扶持<br />\n成日一齊做gym 跑步 打拳 學外語...<br />\n又發覺幾開心 幾自由 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來我既世界先岩岩開始 我本如此 享受下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n非常建議絲打你 接觸多啲大自然 同下fd一齊行下山 做下運動咁 參加啲courses  去旅行...etc。 總好過放假屈係屋企亂諗野 可能你真正既命中注定就係咁而識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d41ac27d701d1bf065206c257894ab75d246515","tid":533362,"uid":137387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T20:24:58.000Z","msg":"係 真心愛過點會做得返朋友<br />\n點會咁容易放低"},{"pid":"b8805f32cb2a1ea1b460c55f64415de75af666f1","tid":533362,"uid":82155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T09:32:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bad8076fea56b31f1c4fc0afb6c0e1d495fea9fd","tid":533362,"uid":45627,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T10:13:58.000Z","msg":"絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你對個男仔都有好感嘅<br />\n我覺得可以同佢講你有咩顧慮<br />\n<br />\n其實件事都唔係發生咗好耐<br />\n俾多少少時間自己啦<br />\n<br />\n你已經好堅強好勁<br />\n加油呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dc691e4927c89b17437ef6e609217daf91f6f8a","tid":533362,"uid":40927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T13:11:57.000Z","msg":"絲打加油！之前有睇過你post"},{"pid":"faf07083f0324c4fc8ef4ed1ea0b1552b6509817","tid":533362,"uid":54597,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8e7685b7343c9aa054ea7c363335ade7c3dcf2b1","tid":533362,"uid":104054,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T20:11:15.000Z","msg":"初初分手真係灰到一個點<br />\n灰爆頹爆喊爆 成日嘆息 好想返到過去 <br />\n<br />\n後尾經過一班大同 中同 既扶持<br />\n成日一齊做gym 跑步 打拳 學外語...<br />\n又發覺幾開心 幾自由 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來我既世界先岩岩開始 我本如此 享受下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n非常建議絲打你 接觸多啲大自然 同下fd一齊行下山 做下運動咁 參加啲courses  去旅行...etc。 總好過放假屈係屋企亂諗野 可能你真正既命中注定就係咁而識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T13:14:33.000Z","msg":"好正氣呀呢個留言"},{"pid":"1696e88c018a52288ae4c64a605b158e3ceb0929","tid":533362,"uid":112800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T13:28:17